{"tid":828923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"ASML看好中國市場：最先進光刻機很快將入華","createTime":"2018-09-20T04:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T07:13:09.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b16e9f7044e919bc58c4ea406c0855c8193f0d3","tid":828923,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:39:06.000Z","msg":"中國集成電路製造年會近日邀請到了光刻機霸主ASML（阿斯麥）中國區總裁沈波參加，他出面解答了一些媒體關心的話題。儘管UMC（聯電）和Globalfoundries（格羅方德，格芯）先後宣布放棄7nm製程及更先進工藝的研發，但ASML依然對EUV光刻機的前景表示樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n此前有消息指出，中芯國際（SMIC）今年已向ASML訂購了一台EUV光刻機，預計明年交付，用於7nm節點。<br />\n<br />\n同時，傳統的沉浸式光刻機方面，沈波稱，今年下半年ASML已開始出貨家族最先進的NXT:2000i，很快會在中國市場上也見到。<br />\n<br />\n另外，媒體早先有報導稱，長江存儲、上海華虹半導體分別向ASML訂購了193納米浸沒式光刻機和193納米雙工件台沉浸式光刻機NXT:1980Di，分別用於存儲晶元製造、晶圓代工。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，ASML今年一二季度的財報顯示，大陸市場的銷售收入佔比達到了20%左右，已與美國持平，且超過了台灣地區。<br />\n<br />\nASML今年的EUV光刻機產能將達到20台，明後兩年將逐步提升到40台。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20180919/28232910.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20180919%2F28232910.html&d=hLOWhBhG0hlTLctC6GWcNaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=254d1304\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20180919/28232910.html</a><br />\n<br />\n已經唔禁售定自吹自擂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47188e7c0fcddb58e332fdf8ac9b09e12ef78fa","tid":828923,"uid":98289,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"可能已經安排晒中國間諜喺間公司入面偷緊資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b67a549d0eb98508bcc790cff7598c2933cc11f","tid":828923,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c28d5dec03feda02518a2eab4801a54b26cfe42","tid":828923,"uid":59518,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:50:49.000Z","msg":"中國區總裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d362ab290af8d33257f538d75911a45ced32a7dc","tid":828923,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"賣架法拉利畀你,唔識揸一樣無用"},{"pid":"f22f2dcbf647a8c4c26a7690e844e115adfaccf6","tid":828923,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n贏国又贏"},{"pid":"f0f90073c23bd2ac7c29c8f3a31cf86752740b77","tid":828923,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:18:56.000Z","msg":"肯賣即係代表中國接近可以自製，最後機會用水魚價搵多一筆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fced815a464168785efb21b4f76ec4c1424bc110","tid":828923,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:20:12.000Z","msg":"怕晶片技術被偷　中國留學生被荷蘭ASML拒聘<br />\n建立時間：2018/08/26 05:32<br />\n中國第二大的電訊設備製造商「中興通訊」（ZTE），因為違反美國的制裁令，私下向伊朗和北韓出售含有美國零件的通訊設備，早前遭到美國商業部重罰，一度陷入「營運休克」。中國政府在這事件後，投入大量金錢，希望減少對美國高端晶片的依賴，同時設法獲取（盜取）歐洲技術。不過，全球最大半導體設備製造商荷蘭艾司摩爾（ASML）近日傳出，在美國的要求下，不再招聘中國籍員工，以防止被中國人竊取高端晶片科技。ASML雖然否認相關傳言，但坦承中國人要從事相關工作，必須先取得美國發出的許可證明。<br />\n<br />\n一名荷蘭求學的中國人，近日上網抱怨，畢業後有意到ASML求職，但後來收到通知，指受到美國政府的限制，ASML不會再聘請中國人。消息曝光後，引發中國網友不滿，對此ASML於周四（23日）澄清，這是不實的傳言，重申ASML招聘員工時，一般不會有國籍限制，歡迎來自各國的工程師。但聲明強調，ASML一直規定，包括中國籍在內的約20國的人士，在從事涉及美國原創技術的工作種類時，必須先取得美國發出的許可證明。<br />\n北京大學國際關係學院教授梁雲祥認為，事件反映中美競爭已白熱化。他指，美國在貿易戰中，當然會要求其他國家，特別是盟國和美國採取同樣步調。因為中國自改革開放以來，「資金及技術依靠西方」，不管ASML的消息是真是假，都對中國高科技領域有影響。梁提醒北京，不要自恃中國有市場，因為即使有商業利益考慮，西方國家還是傾向支持美國。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180826/1418052/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180826%2F1418052%2F&d=hLOWhBhG0hlTLctC6GWcNaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=43babc03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180826%2F1418052%2F&h=ede31955\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180826/1418052/</a><br />\n<br />\n上個月先傳話連中國人都唔請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d258b6ca74de7ae12601d48e87ca1462afb32c28","tid":828923,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:56:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">據悉，ASML今年一二季度的財報顯示，大陸市場的銷售收入佔比達到了20%左右，已與美國持平，且超過了台灣地區</span>。<br />\n<br />\n呢d 出貨週期都拎黎打J,唔通d 廠會不停買機  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知以為支那增長超越台灣 美國<br />\n一睇台灣地區四個字就知支那仔寫<br />\n<br />\n上至下18 第二同第一季，18第一季同17第二季<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/144924_1e562a61fc7578138d11d79413d26b52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F144924_1e562a61fc7578138d11d79413d26b52.png&h=79215117&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/144927_92377ebe01a73bd1029c74233c277000.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F144927_92377ebe01a73bd1029c74233c277000.png&h=8575dc5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9bd3794f72e3370417960b29ace40d40fba8c3a","tid":828923,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d258b6ca74de7ae12601d48e87ca1462afb32c28","tid":828923,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:56:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">據悉，ASML今年一二季度的財報顯示，大陸市場的銷售收入佔比達到了20%左右，已與美國持平，且超過了台灣地區</span>。<br />\n<br />\n呢d 出貨週期都拎黎打J,唔通d 廠會不停買機  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知以為支那增長超越台灣 美國<br />\n一睇台灣地區四個字就知支那仔寫<br />\n<br />\n上至下18 第二同第一季，18第一季同17第二季<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/144924_1e562a61fc7578138d11d79413d26b52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F144924_1e562a61fc7578138d11d79413d26b52.png&h=79215117&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/144927_92377ebe01a73bd1029c74233c277000.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F144927_92377ebe01a73bd1029c74233c277000.png&h=8575dc5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:56:56.000Z","msg":"17第四季先岩"},{"pid":"1945178b3f73a5e58e2afa627d0ce9c6ee225e7f","tid":828923,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"193納米即係有幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d859c12963ed7cbd0d08df1a859d77deac04a4","tid":828923,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1945178b3f73a5e58e2afa627d0ce9c6ee225e7f","tid":828923,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"193納米即係有幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"唔知<br />\n<br />\n但以前聽開呢間野一係技術封鎖禁售中國<br />\n<br />\n一係就只賣舊幾代既機"},{"pid":"9ed1d0f1de65c37ec4d13cd768568c6c3900ca48","tid":828923,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:13:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾侵"}]}